```py
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib. pyplot as plt

data = pd.read_csv("diabetes.csv")

plt. plot(data['Preg'])
plt. plot(data['age'])
plt. title("Line Plot")
plt. xlabel('Preg')
plt. label('age')
plt. show()
```

```py
from bokeh.plotting import figure, output_file, show
import pandas as pd

graph = figure(title = "Bokeh Bar Chart")
data = pd.read_csv("diabetes.csv")

df = data['age'].value_counts()

graph.line(df, data['age'])
show(graph)
```
